These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, coffee, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, chess, baking, traveling
1. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking soy-milk##7
4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | iced-tea       | lemonade | soy-milk        |
| Hobby      | baking  | chess | traveling        | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, frog, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, handball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the owner of the frog##7
2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
3. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | frog | hamster       | cat         | goldfish     |
| Sport   | golf   | sailing | handball | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, horror, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, electronic, funk
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the fan of hip-hop##7
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of funk and the person watching fantasy movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | zombie | horror | sports  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | hip-hop  | funk   | r&b |

