.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, cooking, puzzles, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, cycling, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's hobby is photography##7
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | singing | photography       | puzzles |
| Sport   | rowing      | cricket   | cycling | ice-hockey  |

