.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, writing, magic-tricks, singing
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, indonesian, mexican, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the turkish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
5. the turkish is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | sudoku   | singing | writing |
| Nationality   | japanese      | indonesian | turkish      | mexican |

