.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, fanta, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, argentine, polish
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the argentine is the person drinking cola##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the polish##3
6. the polish is somewhere between the japanese and the canadian##7
7. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | tea | soy-milk      | fanta | cola     |
| Nationality   | japanese    | polish | canadian   | argentine |

