2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the russian##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
4. the pakistani is somewhere between the person eating cucumber and the person eating eggplant##7
5. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person eating eggplant##5
6. the pakistani is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | nectarine    | cucumber   | carrot | eggplant  |
| Nationality   | australian | polish | pakistani    | russian |

