2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
3. the japanese is the owner of the frog##1
4. the german is somewhere between the japanese and the mexican##7
5. the canadian is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | german | canadian | mexican |
| Pet           | frog   | bird    | guinea-pig       | mouse  |

