2. the person watching zombie movies is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
3. the owner of the frog is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
4. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the person watching animation movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | romance | zombie | time-travel |
| Pet           | goldfish    | frog   | goat  | hedgehog      |

