.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, dancing, board-games, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, tram, jet-ski
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | woodworking | rock-climbing | dancing | board-games |
| Transport   | ship   | jet-ski      | quad-bike        | tram  |

