4. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | sprite | lemonade | milk   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | techno   | country | trance |

