4. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
6. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
