.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, frog, guinea-pig, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, train, taxi, snowmobile
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the owner of the frog##7
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | frog    | guinea-pig | mouse     | pony |
| Transport   | taxi | snowmobile  | train | trike |

 